{"input": "已知$5x^{2}y^{2}+y^{4}=1$（$x,y∈R$），则$x^{2}+y^{2}$的最小值是______.", "output": "$\\\\because 5x^{2}y^{2}+y^{4}=1$，$\\\\therefore y\\\\neq0$ 且 $x^{2}=\\\\frac{1-y^{4}}{5y^{2}}$$\\\\therefore x^{2}+y^{2}=\\\\frac{1-y^{4}}{5y^{2}}+y^{2}=\\\\frac{1}{5y^{2}}+\\\\frac{4y^{2}}{5}≥2\\\\sqrt{\\\\frac{1}{5y^{2}}\\\\cdot\\\\frac{4y^{2}}{5}}=\\\\frac{4}{5}$，当且仅当$\\\\frac{1}{5y^{2}}=\\\\frac{4y^{2}}{5}$，即$x^{2}=\\\\frac{3}{10}$，$y^{2}=\\\\frac{1}{2}$时取等号.$\\\\therefore x^{2}+y^{2}$的最小值为$\\\\frac{4}{5}$. 故答案为：$\\\\frac{4}{5}$."}
